  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a deep pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and let them sizzle for 30 seconds.",
    "Add onion, green chilies, and salt. Saute until onion is translucent.",
    "Add rice and water to the pan. Stir well.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil. Reduce heat to low and cover.",
    "Simmer for 15 minutes.",
    "Melt Mars bars in a separate pan over low heat.",
    "Fluff the rice mixture with a fork.",
    "Add the melted Mars bars to the rice mixture.",
    "Mix well and transfer to a banana leaf.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve hot."
